title: Manchester United legend Ole Gunnar Solskjaer rejects Norway boss job following Per-Mathias Hogmo’s resignation
text:
Gunnar say no Manchester United legend Ole Gunnar Solskjaer rejects Norway boss job following Per-Mathias Hogmo’s resignation 
Former boss stood down in November 2016 following a poor start to their World Cup qualifying campaign with the Old Trafford super-sub distancing himself from potential role By Dave Fraser
